ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: An excellent course given the amount of material synthesized and the potential for a high-profile publication; however, prospective students should carefully consider how much free-time they will have to dedicate to this class
Yes I strongly recommend this course, because it is a real test to improve the personal way brain and the personal ability to work with a team

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: An interesting paper should result from this project; however, it is largely irrelevant for my research interests.
This course was the opportunity to learn new methods and to deepen my knowledge on a group, before not considered in my background
